kinds of experiments.

00:11:25.640 --> 00:11:27.400 align:middle line:90%
But they are ongoing.

00:11:27.400 --> 00:11:30.430 align:middle line:84%
There was a contract,
it was a request

00:11:30.430 --> 00:11:34.020 align:middle line:84%
for proposals that expired in
2009 by the Air Force looking

00:11:34.020 --> 00:11:37.000 align:middle line:84%
for new modeling and then the
most recent DARPA contracts

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:39.010 align:middle line:84%
I just mentioned in
California looking

00:11:39.010 --> 00:11:41.480 align:middle line:84%
for methods of sort
of mapping the brain.

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:44.450 align:middle line:84%
In fact, MIT's "Technology
