00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:58.300 align:middle line:90%
or effects.

00:11:58.300 --> 00:11:59.770 align:middle line:84%
And this is what
the Air Force now

00:11:59.770 --> 00:12:03.835 align:middle line:84%
