a major article was written in

00:12:03.835 --> 00:12:08.650 align:middle line:84%
June 2004 in "Technology
Horizons," which

00:12:08.650 --> 00:12:11.220 align:middle line:84%
the article was written by the
electromagnetic directorate

00:12:11.220 --> 00:12:13.250 align:middle line:84%
of the Air Force, which
most people don't even

00:12:13.250 --> 00:12:14.910 align:middle line:84%
know such an
organization exists.

00:12:14.910 --> 00:12:17.285 align:middle line:84%
But these are the people that
really get involved in this

00:12:17.285 --> 00:12:19.650 align:middle line:84%
and looking at how to
model energetically

00:12:19.650 --> 00:12:22.410 align:middle line:84%
the human body and mind
and be able to affect

00:12:22.410 --> 00:12:24.840 align:middle line:84%
the basic organs of the
body or the mind itself.

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:28.050 align:middle line:84%
And that's really the
big shift in technology,

00:12:28.050 --> 00:12:31.350 align:middle line:84%
what they call a revolution in
military affairs, a shift where

00:12:31.350 --> 00:12:35.190 align:middle line:84%
energy instead of bullets and
bombs become the primary mover,

00:12:35.190 --> 00:12:37.110 align:middle line:84%
whether you're attacking
hardware, software,

00:12:37.110 --> 00:12:38.099 align:middle line:90%
or the human operator.

