00:14:41.340 --> 00:14:42.630 align:middle line:90%
And it's really quite simple.

00:14:42.630 --> 00:14:44.960 align:middle line:90%
It can be done very simply.

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:47.820 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: I somewhat find it
