00:21:33.452 --> 00:21:34.910 align:middle line:84%
Earth-penetrating
tomography, which

00:21:34.910 --> 00:21:36.820 align:middle line:84%
happens to work within
the same frequency

00:21:36.820 --> 00:21:39.160 align:middle line:84%
range as predominant
brainwave activity.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:43.110 align:middle line:84%
And this is where they use
a signal-- high frequency

00:21:43.110 --> 00:21:45.920 align:middle line:84%
signal is literally pulsed
into the ionosphere, which

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:47.830 align:middle line:84%
is about 30 miles above
the Earth's surface.

00:21:47.830 --> 00:21:49.540 align:middle line:84%
It begins to punch
the ionosphere,

00:21:49.540 --> 00:21:51.440 align:middle line:84%
and as it does the
ionosphere begins

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:54.235 align:middle line:84%
to vibrate in harmony with
that punch or that pulse rate.

00:21:54.235 --> 00:21:55.110 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Boom, boom.

00:21:55.110 --> 00:21:55.390 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: Right.

00:21:55.390 --> 00:21:57.160 align:middle line:84%
And now that changes
the ionosphere.

00:21:57.160 --> 00:22:00.440 align:middle line:84%
This electromagnetic
layer begins

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:02.600 align:middle line:84%
to act as a broadcast
antenna, sends

00:22:02.600 --> 00:22:05.030 align:middle line:84%
an ELF, an Extremely
Low Frequency signal,

00:22:05.030 --> 00:22:06.800 align:middle line:90%
back through the Earth and sea.

00:22:06.800 --> 00:22:10.180 align:middle line:84%
But that same ELF can
couple with the human mind

00:22:10.180 --> 00:22:13.990 align:middle line:84%
in a way that changes people's
emotional state from highly

00:22:13.990 --> 00:22:16.650 align:middle line:90%
passive to aggressive.

