00:22:23.450 --> 00:22:25.040 align:middle line:84%
was talking about
and what Brzezinski

00:22:25.040 --> 00:22:26.520 align:middle line:84%
was talking about
in his writings.

00:22:26.520 --> 00:22:29.920 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: What is the range
