make that guy rob a bank or do

00:52:09.250 --> 00:52:10.500 align:middle line:90%
something like that?

00:52:10.500 --> 00:52:12.541 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: The kind of
technologies we're talking

00:52:12.541 --> 00:52:15.430 align:middle line:84%
about, yeah, that's
exactly what you could do.

00:52:15.430 --> 00:52:18.200 align:middle line:84%
With acoustic heterodyning,
you would need line of sight.

00:52:18.200 --> 00:52:20.060 align:middle line:90%
You'd need actual contact.

00:52:20.060 --> 00:52:22.630 align:middle line:84%
But the idea that
there's a number of ways

00:52:22.630 --> 00:52:26.370 align:middle line:84%
to carry a signal, any
electromagnetic carrier, this

00:52:26.370 --> 00:52:27.150 align:middle line:90%
is very, very--

00:52:27.150 --> 00:52:28.665 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: And the poor person
at home who would have no idea

00:52:28.665 --> 00:52:29.070 align:middle line:90%
what was happening.

00:52:29.070 --> 00:52:29.861 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: No clue.

00:52:29.861 --> 00:52:32.459 align:middle line:84%
And again, you
have predisposition

00:52:32.459 --> 00:52:33.875 align:middle line:84%
or some conditioning
to get people

00:52:33.875 --> 00:52:36.182 align:middle line:84%
to do something they
normally wouldn't do.

00:52:36.182 --> 00:52:39.780 align:middle line:84%
But yeah, this is, again, the
possibility of that change,

00:52:39.780 --> 00:52:41.900 align:middle line:84%
or things that aren't
really so relevant, maybe

00:52:41.900 --> 00:52:43.970 align:middle line:84%
the decision on do
you vote for this guy

00:52:43.970 --> 00:52:45.580 align:middle line:90%
or do you vote for that guy.

00:52:45.580 --> 00:52:47.755 align:middle line:90%
And we hear this way too much.

00:52:47.755 --> 00:52:50.510 align:middle line:84%
It's a choice between
two evils, all right?

00:52:50.510 --> 00:52:54.700 align:middle line:84%
So those kinds of push
events to create a change

00:52:54.700 --> 00:52:58.381 align:middle line:84%
in outcomes, that's where
this gets manipulative.

00:52:58.381 --> 00:53:00.880 align:middle line:84%
That's where it violates what
I think are the ethical rules.

00:53:00.880 --> 00:53:01.990 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Absolutely
unbelievable.

00:53:01.990 --> 00:53:04.540 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: In fact, even mind
control as an issue was a cover

00:53:04.540 --> 00:53:10.040 align:middle line:84%
