2002-- in "The Economist"

00:53:10.040 --> 00:53:11.790 align:middle line:90%
on the ethics of mind control.

00:53:11.790 --> 00:53:13.930 align:middle line:84%
Because even now
11 years ago they

00:53:13.930 --> 00:53:15.740 align:middle line:84%
were looking at the
ethical consequences

00:53:15.740 --> 00:53:17.490 align:middle line:84%
of exactly what we're
talking about today.

00:53:17.490 --> 00:53:19.490 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: So if we drove
by the masses and went,

00:53:19.490 --> 00:53:23.000 align:middle line:84%
