And it would work.

00:53:25.900 --> 00:53:27.910 align:middle line:84%
And here's the thing
about it is when

00:53:27.910 --> 00:53:29.820 align:middle line:84%
you've talked about the
technologies in Japan

00:53:29.820 --> 00:53:31.700 align:middle line:84%
for dissuading
shoplifters, now imagine

00:53:31.700 --> 00:53:34.029 align:middle line:84%
if that store got
the idea, well, this

00:53:34.029 --> 00:53:36.070 align:middle line:84%
is a good way to get rid
of obsolete merchandise.

00:53:36.070 --> 00:53:36.750 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Yeah.

00:53:36.750 --> 00:53:37.360 align:middle line:90%
That's right.

00:53:37.360 --> 00:53:39.234 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: Now is that
the right thing to do?

00:53:39.234 --> 00:53:40.947 align:middle line:84%
I think most people
would agree not.

00:53:40.947 --> 00:53:42.530 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: But what
a great sales tool.

00:53:42.530 --> 00:53:43.000 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: Yeah.

00:53:43.000 --> 00:53:44.680 align:middle line:84%
You might end up with
a fluorescent tie,

00:53:44.680 --> 00:53:46.530 align:middle line:84%
