00:53:52.987 --> 00:53:53.820 align:middle line:90%
>> AUDIENCE: Noelle.

00:53:53.820 --> 00:53:55.430 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Noelle, have a seat.

00:53:55.430 --> 00:53:56.457 align:middle line:90%
