00:53:56.457 --> 00:53:57.040 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: Hi.

00:53:57.040 --> 00:53:57.700 align:middle line:90%
Nice to meet you.

00:53:57.700 --> 00:53:58.250 align:middle line:84%
>> AUDIENCE:
Pleasure to meet you.

00:53:58.250 --> 00:53:59.330 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Nick, do what you do.

00:53:59.330 --> 00:53:59.810 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: All right.

00:53:59.810 --> 00:54:00.540 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: You're not going
to hurt her now, right?

00:54:00.540 --> 00:54:02.130 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: No, this isn't
going to hurt at all.

00:54:02.130 --> 00:54:02.890 align:middle line:84%
What I'm going to
do is I'm going

00:54:02.890 --> 00:54:04.750 align:middle line:84%
to place these or
ask you to place

00:54:04.750 --> 00:54:06.890 align:middle line:90%
these just on your cheeks.

00:54:06.890 --> 00:54:09.581 align:middle line:84%
Block your ears at the same
time so that you can kind of

00:54:09.581 --> 00:54:10.830 align:middle line:90%
perceive where this signal is.

00:54:10.830 --> 00:54:14.679 align:middle line:84%
And then tell everyone what
you hear and where it's at.

00:54:14.679 --> 00:54:19.772 align:middle line:90%


00:54:19.772 --> 00:54:20.730 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Is it on now?

00:54:20.730 --> 00:54:21.270 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: It's on.

00:54:21.270 --> 00:54:22.353 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, I've got it running.

00:54:22.353 --> 00:54:24.627 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: OK.

00:54:24.627 --> 00:54:25.710 align:middle line:90%
>> AUDIENCE: I hear music.

00:54:25.710 --> 00:54:26.690 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: All right.

00:54:26.690 --> 00:54:27.390 align:middle line:90%
And where is it?

00:54:27.390 --> 00:54:28.890 align:middle line:84%
>> AUDIENCE: But
it's weird, though,

00:54:28.890 --> 00:54:31.160 align:middle line:84%
because you don't really
