00:54:31.160 --> 00:54:31.680 align:middle line:90%
It's like right--

00:54:31.680 --> 00:54:32.240 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Is it strange?

00:54:32.240 --> 00:54:33.823 align:middle line:84%
>> AUDIENCE: It's
right in your brain.

00:54:33.823 --> 00:54:35.330 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:54:35.330 --> 00:54:37.974 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Is it almost like
