00:54:42.559 --> 00:54:43.100 align:middle line:90%
in your head.

00:54:43.100 --> 00:54:43.875 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: What kind
of music was it?

00:54:43.875 --> 00:54:44.960 align:middle line:84%
>> AUDIENCE: It was
classical music.

00:54:44.960 --> 00:54:45.460 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: Yes, it is.

00:54:45.460 --> 00:54:45.750 align:middle line:90%
>> AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:54:45.750 --> 00:54:46.720 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Try it on me.

00:54:46.720 --> 00:54:47.594 align:middle line:90%
>> BEGICH: All right.

00:54:47.594 --> 00:54:49.640 align:middle line:90%
Block your ears tightly, George.

00:54:49.640 --> 00:54:51.806 align:middle line:84%
Just block your ears so you
don't have the external.

00:54:51.806 --> 00:54:54.542 align:middle line:90%


00:54:54.542 --> 00:54:55.500 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: That's weird.

00:54:55.500 --> 00:54:57.760 align:middle line:90%
I have a talking cheek.

00:54:57.760 --> 00:54:59.230 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:54:59.230 --> 00:55:00.900 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: And the
thing about this,

00:55:00.900 --> 00:55:02.680 align:middle line:84%
when you think
about this kind of--

00:55:02.680 --> 00:55:03.100 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: That is strange.

00:55:03.100 --> 00:55:05.540 align:middle line:84%
>> BEGICH: --technology, and
it's what they used to call

00:55:05.540 --> 00:55:08.080 align:middle line:84%
infrasound, the idea of
putting sound into the body

00:55:08.080 --> 00:55:10.700 align:middle line:90%
in a different way.

00:55:10.700 --> 00:55:13.376 align:middle line:84%
This was extraordinarily
compelling

00:55:13.376 --> 00:55:15.250 align:middle line:84%
when we presented to
the European Parliament,

00:55:15.250 --> 00:55:17.750 align:middle line:84%
because they'd heard about,
they'd read about literature,

00:55:17.750 --> 00:55:19.520 align:middle line:90%
but no one ever had tried one.

00:55:19.520 --> 00:55:20.720 align:middle line:90%
It made a huge difference.

00:55:20.720 --> 00:55:25.210 align:middle line:84%
Because this is made by a
non-governmental technician.

00:55:25.210 --> 00:55:29.051 align:middle line:84%
This is not something coming out
of a billion-dollar laboratory.

00:55:29.051 --> 00:55:30.050 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: That is weird.

00:55:30.050 --> 00:55:32.652 align:middle line:84%
Well, let's first of
