>> BEGICH: On a regular basis
at a level where most people

00:59:28.870 --> 00:59:29.870 align:middle line:90%
aren't even aware of it.

00:59:29.870 --> 00:59:30.953 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: What technology.

